Donation App 

This is a Figma design for a donation app that allows users to donate to various charitable organizations.

Getting Started
To get started with the Figma design, follow these steps:

Clone the repository or download the Figma file.
Open the Figma file in Figma.
Explore the various screens and components in the design.
Customize the design to fit your needs.
Screens
The Figma design includes the following screens:

Home screen
Donation screen
Payment screen
Thank you screen
Components
The Figma design includes the following reusable components:

Buttons
Inputs
Cards
Icons
Typography
Dependencies
The Figma design does not have any dependencies.

Contributing
If you would like to contribute to the Figma design, please follow these steps:

Fork the repository.
Create a new branch for your changes.
Make your changes to the Figma file.
Submit a pull request.


Credits
The Figma design was created by Anika Santiago and Axell Balawitan
